obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `This Act may be called the Bihar Land Reforms Laws (Regulating Mines and Minerals)`
  line `Validation Act, 1969.`
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (72667)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title `Validation of certain Bihar State laws and action taken and things done connected therewith.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_18_43_00008_196942_1673602840703&sectionId=72667&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_18_43_00008_196942_1673602840703
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `(1) The laws specified in the Schedule shall be, and shall be deemed always to have been, as valid as if the`
  line `provisions contained therein had been enacted by Parliament.`
  line
  line `(2) Notwithstanding any judgment, decree or order of any court, all action taken, things done, rules`
  line `made, notifications issued or purported to have been taken, done, made or issued and rents or royalties`
  line `realised under any such laws shall be deemed to have been validly taken, done, made, issued or realised, as`
  line `the case may be, as if this section had been in force at all material times when such action was taken, things,`
  line `were done, rules were made, notifications were issued, or rents or royalties were realised, and no suit or`
  line `other proceeding shall be maintained or continued in any court for the refund of rents or royalties realised`
  line `under any such laws.`
  line
  line `(3) For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that nothing in sub-section (2) shall be construed as`
  line `preventing any person from claiming refund of any rents or royalties paid by him in excess of the amount`
  line `due from him under any such laws.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
